I think most people (college or not) would benefit from reading this book and trying out Oz's common sense plan.
Older readers might need a little less food overall and might not opt to go out and have a snowball fight to burn calories, but the basics are here for a good lifestyle plan that isn't painful and does work.
This would be a great book for anyone (females more so) headed off to college or in college.
Oz has dealt with being overweight.
